SLEEP:
    We can sleep the thread for some time.
    Thread.sleep(milliseconds).
    Thread.currentThread().getName() //will tell which thread is getting called.


EXECUTION ORDER:
    1. Order of execution is not guaranteed.
    2. We can set name using Thread.currentThread.setName()



IF we want to implement a class through a runanble interface.

STEP#1
create the class implementing RunnableInterace.
define run method on it.


STEP#2
Create a Thread object and pass the object on it.
call the start method through it.
